OL,10,     Fand plenty of afternoon gossip!
OL,11,G1500 Castle
OL,12,     FWhen a rising young pop star is
OL,13,     Ffound dead in an alley, Castle and
OL,14,     FBeckett delve into the victim's
OL,15,     Fout-of-control hard-partying
OL,16,     Flifestyle.
